1
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:09,718
- What are you doing?
- What about you?

2
00:00:09,718 --> 00:00:13,100
I warned you. I told you to keep
your daughter away from my son.

3
00:00:13,100 --> 00:00:16,335
What are you talking about you?
Your son was already doing music.

4
00:00:16,335 --> 00:00:18,721
You didn't know that, as his mother?

5
00:00:18,721 --> 00:00:20,474
Okay, bring it on!

6
00:00:20,474 --> 00:00:24,434
Your ex-husband and your daughter
are crapping all over us!

7
00:00:25,231 --> 00:00:26,791
Crapping all over you?

8
00:00:28,405 --> 00:00:31,045
Okay, bring it on!
I'm not scared!

9
00:00:31,045 --> 00:00:32,335
Bring it on!

10
00:00:33,632 --> 00:00:35,342
You!

11
00:00:35,342 --> 00:00:36,975
Stop!

12
00:00:38,170 --> 00:00:40,621
Let go of my hair!

13
00:00:40,621 --> 00:00:42,100
You let go!

14
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:43,350
What's wrong with you?

15
00:00:43,350 --> 00:00:44,578
Do Kyung!

16
00:00:44,578 --> 00:00:47,000
Hey! Let go!

17
00:00:47,299 --> 00:00:51,299
Subtitles by DramaFever

18
00:00:52,393 --> 00:00:53,728
Honey!

19
00:00:55,009 --> 00:00:56,353
Are you okay, Honey?

20
00:00:59,079 --> 00:01:00,801
Calm down, Honey!

21
00:01:03,692 --> 00:01:05,055
Let go!

22
00:01:05,055 --> 00:01:06,317
I said let go!

23
00:01:06,317 --> 00:01:07,731
You let go first.

24
00:01:07,731 --> 00:01:10,566
Let go, both of you! Calm down!

25
00:01:10,566 --> 00:01:12,965
Let go on the count of three!

26
00:01:12,965 --> 00:01:15,950
One, two, three!

27
00:01:15,950 --> 00:01:17,671
Three!

28
00:01:17,671 --> 00:01:19,947
You!

29
00:01:20,495 --> 00:01:22,902
What's wrong with you?
This is embarrassing!

30
00:01:22,902 --> 00:01:24,463
She won't let go!

31
00:01:24,463 --> 00:01:25,668
What about you?

32
00:01:25,668 --> 00:01:28,373
Eun Ok, please stop.
Do Kyung is a patient!

33
00:01:29,293 --> 00:01:30,891
Oh, Gi Bum!

34
00:01:30,891 --> 00:01:32,487
Your nose, your nose!

35
00:01:32,534 --> 00:01:34,522
My nose? What about it? Huh?

36
00:01:34,522 --> 00:01:35,855
Ah!

37
00:01:35,855 --> 00:01:38,418
Blood! From both my nostrils!

38
00:01:38,418 --> 00:01:39,612
Geez!

39
00:01:40,909 --> 00:01:42,245
Let go!

40
00:01:42,245 --> 00:01:45,362
Oh, my nose! My nose!

41
00:01:45,362 --> 00:01:46,581
Let go!

42
00:01:46,581 --> 00:01:48,706
Gi Bum! Oh, no!

43
00:01:48,706 --> 00:01:52,760
Gi Bum, don't die! Don't die, Gi Bum!

44
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:55,472
This is bad! What should we do?

45
00:01:55,472 --> 00:01:57,472
- Ah!
- My goodness!

46
00:01:57,472 --> 00:01:59,245
Don't die!

47
00:01:59,245 --> 00:02:00,245
Gi Bum!

48
00:02:00,245 --> 00:02:02,840
My nose is bleeding!

49
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:03,941
Louder...

50
00:02:03,941 --> 00:02:04,941
Oh no!

51
00:02:07,972 --> 00:02:10,132
It finally stopped.

52
00:02:10,132 --> 00:02:12,388
Why did you try to stop us?

53
00:02:12,388 --> 00:02:14,852
I was going to battle it out this time.

54
00:02:14,852 --> 00:02:17,540
How dare she hit my precious daughter?

55
00:02:17,540 --> 00:02:19,701
If only my arm was in shape...

56
00:02:19,701 --> 00:02:23,131
That's right. Is your arm okay?

57
00:02:23,131 --> 00:02:24,189
Huh?

58
00:02:28,167 --> 00:02:30,698
I guess it got better after
I warmed up my body a bit.

59
00:02:30,698 --> 00:02:33,217
Were you just pretending?

60
00:02:33,217 --> 00:02:36,328
Stay still. I need to wipe your face off.

61
00:02:36,328 --> 00:02:39,646
Geez. Your face is covered with blood!

62
00:02:39,646 --> 00:02:41,068
Geez.

63
00:02:41,736 --> 00:02:42,814
Blow.

64
00:02:44,471 --> 00:02:46,604
Oh, Hyun Jee.

65
00:02:47,442 --> 00:02:50,544
Oh... where have you been?

66
00:02:51,741 --> 00:02:54,207
I was with Sung Min.

67
00:02:55,177 --> 00:02:57,284
All of this happened because of me.

68
00:02:57,284 --> 00:02:59,364
I'm sorry, Mom, Dad.

69
00:02:59,364 --> 00:03:02,479
Don't say that.
You did nothing wrong.

70
00:03:02,479 --> 00:03:06,200
Right. The adults were wrong.
We ruined your show.

71
00:03:06,200 --> 00:03:09,804
Offering a show to
the public is a great thing!

72
00:03:09,804 --> 00:03:14,463
Your singing totally mesmerized me.

73
00:03:17,854 --> 00:03:20,550
By the way, Hyun Jee...

74
00:03:20,550 --> 00:03:22,789
Do you want to do music for film?

75
00:03:23,896 --> 00:03:25,971
Why music for film, specifically?

76
00:03:25,971 --> 00:03:31,429
Oh... you didn't know that I became the
CEO of a movie production company.

77
00:03:31,429 --> 00:03:32,981
Never mind.

78
00:03:32,981 --> 00:03:36,942
You are a beauty just like your mom.

79
00:03:36,942 --> 00:03:38,925
Do you want to be
in a movie with your mom?

80
00:03:40,473 --> 00:03:44,675
No, thank you. I retired a long time ago.

81
00:03:44,675 --> 00:03:48,044
Why not? You'd be good in action movies.
You can fight.

82
00:03:48,044 --> 00:03:51,352
Let go! Let go! Ah!

83
00:03:53,140 --> 00:03:54,987
It's going to be a hit!

84
00:03:56,069 --> 00:03:57,811
Stop it already.

85
00:03:57,811 --> 00:03:59,711
You should go home.

86
00:03:59,711 --> 00:04:01,602
I'm good. I can go later.

87
00:04:01,602 --> 00:04:03,659
I meant she and I need to go home.

88
00:04:03,659 --> 00:04:05,526
I see...

89
00:04:05,671 --> 00:04:06,961
That's right.

90
00:04:08,842 --> 00:04:10,675
Since when?

91
00:04:11,979 --> 00:04:13,175
Let's talk later.

92
00:04:13,175 --> 00:04:15,540
No. Answer me now.

93
00:04:15,540 --> 00:04:16,550
Mom...

94
00:04:16,550 --> 00:04:19,251
Did Hyun Jee talk you
into doing it together?

95
00:04:19,955 --> 00:04:22,447
It's not like that.
It has nothing to do with her.

96
00:04:22,447 --> 00:04:26,067
You were a good student. Why are
you suddenly doing strange things?

97
00:04:26,067 --> 00:04:28,310
Do you know how I feel now?

98
00:04:28,310 --> 00:04:31,242
It feels like the sky is falling down.

99
00:04:32,353 --> 00:04:34,235
This is big.

100
00:04:34,235 --> 00:04:38,552
Well... calm down.
Let's hear what he has to say first.

101
00:04:38,552 --> 00:04:39,983
I don't want to hear it.

102
00:04:39,983 --> 00:04:42,310
Stop that strange stuff
and focus on studying.

103
00:04:42,310 --> 00:04:44,896
If you study hard for just one more
year, you'll go to Seoul University--

104
00:04:44,896 --> 00:04:46,997
Stop talking about Seoul University!

105
00:04:49,502 --> 00:04:52,555
I won't go to Seoul University.
I don't want to.

106
00:04:55,889 --> 00:04:59,754
You have no interest in what
I like, or what I want to do.

107
00:04:59,754 --> 00:05:03,822
You always talk about Seoul University.
Have you ever asked me about my dreams?

108
00:05:06,620 --> 00:05:09,392
I kept it a secret all this time,
but I won't do that anymore.

109
00:05:09,392 --> 00:05:11,507
I will keep doing music.

110
00:05:13,497 --> 00:05:15,639
You've gone insane.

111
00:05:15,639 --> 00:05:19,093
Okay, I'll help you come to your senses.

112
00:05:19,850 --> 00:05:20,889
Honey!

113
00:05:20,889 --> 00:05:22,975
- Mom...
- Step aside!

114
00:05:25,483 --> 00:05:26,694
Mom.

115
00:05:26,694 --> 00:05:27,757
I said, step aside.

116
00:05:27,757 --> 00:05:29,451
Please don't do this.

117
00:05:29,451 --> 00:05:30,687
Stay away. You'll get hurt!

118
00:05:30,687 --> 00:05:32,483
- Mom!
- Go!

119
00:05:32,939 --> 00:05:35,357
No, don't do that!

120
00:05:36,408 --> 00:05:38,791
Tae Soo! Tae Soo!

121
00:05:39,314 --> 00:05:40,495
Oh no!

122
00:05:40,495 --> 00:05:42,396
I said step aside!

123
00:06:00,577 --> 00:06:02,398
What are you doing?

124
00:06:02,398 --> 00:06:04,108
Give me that.

125
00:06:04,108 --> 00:06:05,377
I don't want to.

126
00:06:06,759 --> 00:06:07,843
Give me that.

127
00:06:07,843 --> 00:06:09,846
I don't want to!

128
00:06:09,846 --> 00:06:12,218
You don't see what's going on here?

129
00:06:12,218 --> 00:06:14,415
My cell phone!

130
00:06:14,415 --> 00:06:15,788
I'll call the police!

131
00:06:15,788 --> 00:06:18,060
Soo Min, go to your room!

132
00:06:18,060 --> 00:06:20,718
Why are you doing this to me?
You pay for it!

133
00:06:20,718 --> 00:06:23,444
Stop it! What are you all
doing to your own family?

134
00:06:23,444 --> 00:06:24,788
Mom, can you stay out of it?

135
00:06:24,788 --> 00:06:27,716
Am I not allowed to talk?
You don't respect your mother?

136
00:06:27,716 --> 00:06:28,783
It's not that!

137
00:06:28,783 --> 00:06:30,319
You stay out of it!

138
00:06:30,319 --> 00:06:32,084
What about my phone?

139
00:06:32,084 --> 00:06:33,154
You stay out of it!

140
00:06:33,154 --> 00:06:34,161
It's all your fault!

141
00:06:34,161 --> 00:06:35,255
You made it worse!

142
00:06:35,255 --> 00:06:36,380
Calm down!

143
00:06:36,380 --> 00:06:37,812
How can I calm down?

144
00:06:37,812 --> 00:06:40,466
Stop, stop! Geez!

145
00:06:40,466 --> 00:06:43,141
Do you really have to
do this in front of me?

146
00:06:43,141 --> 00:06:45,726
I won't live much longer!

147
00:06:45,726 --> 00:06:50,593
Geez, where is the Grim Reaper?
Please come get me!

148
00:07:15,144 --> 00:07:17,935
<i>Just in case, here's a
song to cheer you up.</i>

149
00:08:29,663 --> 00:08:33,973
Geez, you are handsome and smart...

150
00:08:33,973 --> 00:08:35,579
And you are good at music!

151
00:08:37,151 --> 00:08:38,806
Who's your dad?

152
00:08:41,144 --> 00:08:43,996
Just scold me like Mom did.

153
00:08:43,996 --> 00:08:46,268
Why would I scold you?

154
00:08:46,268 --> 00:08:50,214
I totally understand you, Sung Min.

155
00:08:50,214 --> 00:08:52,370
You are not allowed to
do what you want to do.

156
00:08:52,370 --> 00:08:54,777
And you have to study,
which is not what you want.

157
00:08:54,777 --> 00:08:56,777
It must be really hard.

158
00:08:58,596 --> 00:09:03,186
However... I understand what
Mom is going through too.

159
00:09:03,186 --> 00:09:09,129
Now I understand what it means to
say that everything has its own time.

160
00:09:09,894 --> 00:09:14,244
Your life can get hard if you don't
study when it's time to study.

161
00:09:19,326 --> 00:09:22,245
Give me some time to think.

162
00:09:24,610 --> 00:09:26,114
Okay.

163
00:09:26,114 --> 00:09:29,192
I will let Mom know.

164
00:09:31,268 --> 00:09:34,323
Cheer up! Up here.

165
00:10:00,503 --> 00:10:04,553
Sugar is the best thing
when you are stressed out.

166
00:10:18,441 --> 00:10:20,513
The song you sent me was pretty good.

167
00:10:20,513 --> 00:10:22,480
Just pretty good?

168
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:25,673
Not amazingly good or shockingly good?

169
00:10:26,902 --> 00:10:30,870
Yes, it was amazing, shockingly great!

170
00:10:33,613 --> 00:10:35,313
It comforted me.

171
00:10:42,782 --> 00:10:44,201
But I'm not sure.

172
00:10:44,201 --> 00:10:47,500
When I think about myself,
I just can't give up music.

173
00:10:47,500 --> 00:10:49,928
But for my mom,
and the rest of my family...

174
00:10:49,928 --> 00:10:53,905
I feel like I should focus wholeheartedly
on studying for one more year.

175
00:10:53,905 --> 00:10:57,813
Then do that. You won't lose music
just because you stopped for one year.

176
00:10:57,849 --> 00:11:02,264
But without music, I don't feel
like studying, or even eating.

177
00:11:02,264 --> 00:11:04,232
Everything I see or hear is meaningless!

178
00:11:04,232 --> 00:11:06,600
Then do what you want to do!

179
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:09,552
Why do you agonize when you've
already made your decision?

180
00:11:11,873 --> 00:11:14,125
Did you know Sung Min was
doing music, Director?

181
00:11:14,125 --> 00:11:15,206
Pardon me?

182
00:11:15,206 --> 00:11:17,985
He often skipped cram school
to perform on the street.

183
00:11:17,985 --> 00:11:19,547
Did you know that?

184
00:11:19,547 --> 00:11:21,874
That was...

185
00:11:21,874 --> 00:11:25,313
Sung Min promised to keep his rank so...

186
00:11:25,313 --> 00:11:26,730
Director!

187
00:11:27,613 --> 00:11:31,284
You asked for his picture so you
could put it on a plank card.

188
00:11:31,284 --> 00:11:33,879
You promised to teach him
as if you were his parent.

189
00:11:33,879 --> 00:11:36,289
Parents wouldn't do that.

190
00:11:36,289 --> 00:11:40,356
You can't do that when he's only one year
away from his college entrance exam.

191
00:11:40,356 --> 00:11:41,956
I'm very sorry.

192
00:11:41,956 --> 00:11:43,658
I'll make it short.

193
00:11:44,250 --> 00:11:47,426
I cannot allow him to
skip cram school again.

194
00:11:47,426 --> 00:11:49,605
Don't tell Sung Min that I was here.

195
00:11:49,605 --> 00:11:53,860
And tell the front desk to text
me every time Sun Min comes here.

196
00:11:54,924 --> 00:11:58,241
I'm sorry if was rude.

197
00:12:06,623 --> 00:12:09,557
Kyung Mee, I can't come
to One Heart today--

198
00:12:10,712 --> 00:12:12,110
What?

199
00:12:12,110 --> 00:12:14,212
<i>Ladies dog fight! That's funny!</i>

200
00:12:14,212 --> 00:12:17,010
<i>I've seen her before.
Isn't she an actress?</i>

201
00:12:17,010 --> 00:12:19,253
<i>Isn't she the chairwoman of One Heart?</i>

202
00:12:19,253 --> 00:12:20,807
<i>One Heart? What's that?</i>

203
00:12:20,807 --> 00:12:24,878
<i>It's a volunteer organization, but
it's just a bunch of gangsters' wives.</i>

204
00:12:24,878 --> 00:12:26,528
You know...

205
00:12:27,422 --> 00:12:31,519
One Heart's reputation, for which
we have worked very hard, was ruined...

206
00:12:31,519 --> 00:12:34,168
By violence.

207
00:12:34,168 --> 00:12:37,756
The chairman would be very proud
of you if he found out, right?

208
00:12:37,756 --> 00:12:40,320
Ma'am, please calm down and sit...

209
00:12:40,320 --> 00:12:41,710
Put it down!

210
00:12:41,710 --> 00:12:43,034
Sure.

211
00:12:47,274 --> 00:12:50,251
I have no right to drink this water.

212
00:12:50,251 --> 00:12:54,636
This kind of incident happened
as soon as I resigned.

213
00:12:54,636 --> 00:12:56,292
Absence of discipline!

214
00:12:56,292 --> 00:12:58,511
Absence of leadership!

215
00:12:58,511 --> 00:13:02,495
That's the only conclusion I can come to!

216
00:13:02,495 --> 00:13:04,918
Please don't say that, Madam.

217
00:13:04,918 --> 00:13:08,275
We were impulsive.

218
00:13:08,275 --> 00:13:10,952
No, it's all my fault.

219
00:13:10,952 --> 00:13:12,143
Yes, it is.

220
00:13:12,143 --> 00:13:14,163
That's what I'm talking about.

221
00:13:14,163 --> 00:13:19,210
It's my fault that I didn't do anything
about what you did to Do Kyung.

222
00:13:19,210 --> 00:13:24,509
If I had corrected the problem then,
this wouldn't have happened.

223
00:13:25,883 --> 00:13:29,735
How will you
take responsibility for this?

224
00:13:30,815 --> 00:13:33,442
I've already resigned from my
honorary chairwoman's position.

225
00:13:33,442 --> 00:13:37,360
Now it's your turn to decide.

226
00:13:38,488 --> 00:13:41,133
Will you choose the
big cause for One Heart?

227
00:13:41,133 --> 00:13:44,041
Will you hold onto your
position for your own glory?

228
00:13:44,041 --> 00:13:46,466
You choose.

229
00:14:00,528 --> 00:14:04,022
Right. It is all my fault.

230
00:14:05,169 --> 00:14:07,321
And I understand what you're saying.

231
00:14:08,552 --> 00:14:10,274
I will...

232
00:14:11,384 --> 00:14:15,424
I will resign from the One Heart
chairwoman position.

233
00:14:18,186 --> 00:14:20,434
Oh... I see.

234
00:14:25,546 --> 00:14:28,393
Okay then... As of now...

235
00:14:28,393 --> 00:14:32,393
Both positions, Honorary Chairwoman,
and Chairwoman, are vacant.

236
00:14:32,393 --> 00:14:37,051
We will elect a new chairwoman right now,
as this is an urgent situation.

237
00:14:37,051 --> 00:14:41,453
All of you are eligible
to run in the election.

238
00:14:41,453 --> 00:14:42,899
And also...

239
00:14:42,899 --> 00:14:47,828
You will choose your next
chairwoman all on your own!

240
00:14:47,828 --> 00:14:50,578
What the heck is going on?

241
00:14:50,578 --> 00:14:53,072
Are we really having an election?

242
00:14:53,072 --> 00:14:57,422
We only have 20 members. But now we
have an emergency planning committee.

243
00:14:57,422 --> 00:15:00,053
My goodness!

244
00:15:00,053 --> 00:15:03,850
I understand how you feel,
but you should have held it together.

245
00:15:03,850 --> 00:15:08,076
It's okay. I don't have the time
to work for One Heart now anyway.

246
00:15:08,076 --> 00:15:10,711
You can have the chairwoman title.

247
00:15:10,711 --> 00:15:13,759
But you're basically a
servant, just doing chores.

248
00:15:13,759 --> 00:15:16,235
Do you really mean it?

249
00:15:18,297 --> 00:15:19,618
What do you mean?

250
00:15:19,618 --> 00:15:21,774
It sounds like you have
no desire for the title.

251
00:15:21,774 --> 00:15:24,282
And how does that interest you?

252
00:15:24,282 --> 00:15:26,745
I'm thinking of running.

253
00:15:31,866 --> 00:15:34,470
You better do something about your wife.

254
00:15:34,470 --> 00:15:37,350
She's totally marred the
company reputation.

255
00:15:38,044 --> 00:15:40,200
Did she fight alone?

256
00:15:40,200 --> 00:15:41,802
Enough.

257
00:15:44,460 --> 00:15:46,201
What about your smart boy?

258
00:15:46,201 --> 00:15:48,273
Hyun Jee wants to be a singer anyway.

259
00:15:48,273 --> 00:15:51,624
But Sung Min was your only hope.
He's the bookworm!

260
00:15:53,772 --> 00:15:54,803
Good morning.

261
00:15:54,803 --> 00:15:56,827
Oh, sit down.

262
00:16:00,937 --> 00:16:03,578
Did you read the script? How was it?

263
00:16:03,578 --> 00:16:05,851
Oh... that is...

264
00:16:07,182 --> 00:16:08,932
Polish it up a little.

265
00:16:08,932 --> 00:16:13,212
Make it a bit more dramatic and sensual.
Wouldn't that be enough?

266
00:16:13,212 --> 00:16:14,212
Just a bit?

267
