You can't turn a watermelon
into a pumpkin by fixing it up a bit.

268
00:16:17,182 --> 00:16:20,855
Why don't you totally change it?

269
00:16:20,855 --> 00:16:23,042
Don't just work on the surface.

270
00:16:23,042 --> 00:16:26,096
A gangster movie is about action anyway.

271
00:16:26,096 --> 00:16:28,509
There's no point in delaying it.

272
00:16:28,509 --> 00:16:31,167
Just worry about whom to cast.

273
00:16:31,167 --> 00:16:34,946
