Don't take your stress out on them.

277
00:16:44,736 --> 00:16:46,198
What did you say?

278
00:16:46,198 --> 00:16:48,750
I've had enough of you.

279
00:16:50,408 --> 00:16:53,033
Are we here to discuss the script?

280
00:16:53,033 --> 00:16:55,001
What's wrong with you?

281
00:16:55,001 --> 00:16:58,376
