283
00:17:03,692 --> 00:17:04,953
Yes.

284
00:17:04,953 --> 00:17:06,148
Okay.

285
00:17:09,078 --> 00:17:11,003
Everyone, follow me.

286
00:17:13,589 --> 00:17:16,275
Geez, we are all dead because of you.

287
00:17:16,275 --> 00:17:19,498
What did I do? Was I wrong?

288
00:17:25,279 --> 00:17:26,626
This car is for you to use.

289
00:17:26,626 --> 00:17:28,799
Are you really giving it to us?

290
00:17:28,799 --> 00:17:30,596
Have you always been
fooled by people throughout life?

291
00:17:30,596 --> 00:17:33,894
You're going to get big.
You better travel safely.

292
00:17:33,894 --> 00:17:37,442
I'm not a stingy man, like someone
who might have always criticized you.

293
00:17:45,596 --> 00:17:47,548
Bub Gyu, give it to them.

294
00:17:47,548 --> 00:17:48,900
Yes, Boss.

295
00:17:48,900 --> 00:17:50,105
Here.

296
00:17:53,071 --> 00:17:54,377
What is this?

297
00:17:54,377 --> 00:17:56,213
You need money.

298
00:17:56,213 --> 00:17:59,893
You don't need to watch your spending.
But watch your mouth.

299
00:18:01,380 --> 00:18:04,224
You don't need to
always speak up, okay?

300
00:18:04,224 --> 00:18:07,678
Don't spend more than 7,000 won per meal.
You could get billed.

301
00:18:07,678 --> 00:18:10,380
Hey, don't be pathetic.

302
00:18:15,144 --> 00:18:18,115
What does a CEO do?

303
00:18:18,115 --> 00:18:21,419
